      "review_summary": "The PR imports `matchesNoProxy` in `src/agents/tools/web-guarded-fetch.ts` and switches NO_PROXY-matched `web_fetch` requests from trusted env-proxy mode to strict guarded fetch mode.\n\nPR surface: Source +4. Total +4 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible: current main already skips EnvHttpProxyAgent when `NO_PROXY` matches, then uses the strict pinned SSRF path. I did not run a live proxy plus local-service reproduction in this read-only review.",
